## Overview

MediaWiki extension: User Drop

View users' statistics (atm just editcount) and drop them based on this.
Code based on the "User Merge and Delete" extension, and Special:Listusers

## Dependencies

For the DELETE functionality, "User Merge and Delete" needs to be installed.

